1. Obavi*la sam sve zadatke na vrijeme. (I completed all the tasks on time.)
2. Oni obavljaju svoje poslove vrlo profesionalno. (They perform their duties very professionally.)
3. Ja obavljam razgovor za posao sutra ujutro. (I have a job interview tomorrow morning.)
4. Moram obaviti kupovinu prije nego što se trgovina zatvori. (I need to do some shopping before the store closes.)
5. Čim obaviš svoje obaveze, možeš ići van s prijateljima. (As soon as you finish your responsibilities, you can go out with your friends.)
6. *Obavio* je mnoge poslove za našu kompaniju. (He completed many tasks for our company.)
7. Nisam još obavio posljednji zadatak na popisu. (I haven't completed the last task on the list yet.)
8. Neka osoba će obaviti razgovor s tobom uskoro. (Someone will conduct an interview with you soon.)
9. Pročitao sam knjigu nakon što sam obavio svoje obaveze. (I read a book after I finished my responsibilities.)
10. Ne mogu obaviti taj zadatak sam, trebat će mi pomoć. (I can't complete that task alone, I'll need help.)

Note: The word "obavim" is only used in the first sentence as the base form. The other forms of the verb "obavljati" are used in the other sentences.